These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, cucumber, papaya
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, electronic, house, r&b
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, goat, turtle
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, march, april, november
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is the fan of electronic##1
 2. the person eating cucumber is the fan of house##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 5. the person eating banana is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 8. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the fan of house##5
 9. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
10. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
11. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the right of the person eating papaya##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Food          | papaya     | banana   | apple | cucumber |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | blues    | r&b   | house    |
| Pet           | goat       | turtle   | cat   | bird     |
| Birthday     | march       | september | november  | april      |

