.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, july, october, april
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, martial-arts, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, hip-hop, rock, techno
4 different pets are kept: dog, lizard, pony, turtle
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 2. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
 3. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the fan of hip-hop##5
 4. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 6. the owner of the turtle is between the fan of techno and the fan of rock##2
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 8. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
 9. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
10. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is the owner of the dog##1
12. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
| Birthday          | april    | october      | july   | january |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | martial-arts | horror | satire  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | rock         | blues  | techno  |
| Pet           | pony      | dog          | turtle | lizard  |

