 3. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 4. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 5. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the futuristic house##5
 6. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
 7. the tower house is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 8. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 9. the person driving the taxi is the fan of dubstep##1
10. the fan of d&b is in an even position##4
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
12. the futuristic house is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |      4       |
