 3. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the thai##3
 5. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
 7. the german is on the far left##1
