.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, punk, country, d&b
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, thriller, zombie
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, skateboard, snowmobile, taxi
 1. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 3. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the fan of punk is between the fan of country and the person watching zombie movies##2
 6. the person watching thriller movies is in an odd position##4
 7. the fan of country is the person watching disaster movies##1
 8. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
11. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
13. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | water      | hot-chocolate | coffee     |
| Music-Genre           | d&b   | electronic  | punk        | country |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy     | zombie     | thriller      | disaster   |
| Transport     | skateboard | snowmobile | taxi          | roller     |

