.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, lime, tomato, watermelon
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, mechanic, social-worker, teacher
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, orchid, poppy, aconite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, punk, soul
 1. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person who growsorchid##5
 2. the fan of soul is the person eating blueberry##1
 3. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5
 4. the architect is in an even position##4
 5. the mechanic is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 6. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5
 7. the social-worker is the person who growsaconite##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
 9. the fan of punk is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
10. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
11. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
12. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | blueberry | tomato  | watermelon    | lime       |
| Job           | mechanic  | teacher | social-worker | architect  |
| Flower   | orchid    | poppy   | aconite  | sunflower     |
| Music-Genre   | soul      | punk    | gospel        | electronic |

 